title: Alan Moore Collection III-  Image - Awesome Comics
description:
So this is me breaking apart my Massive 29 gig Alan Moore Collection into much easier to to download pieces.

This torrent is only a bit over 2 gigs and has all the comics Alan Moore while at Image/Awesome Comics

Titles include 1963, Deathblow, Byblows, Fire From Heaven, Glory, Judgement Day, Nightjar, Shadowhawk, Spawn, Supreme, WildC.A.T.s, Youngblood

Please enjoy. Please please please donate to this Kickstarter
